headline: Texas Capital upgrades Texas Pacific Land on data center, energy transition bets
summary: Investing.com -- Texas Capital on Thursday upgraded Texas Pacific Land (NYSE:TPL) Corp to Buy and raised its price target to $1,280 saying it has a growing confidence in the landowner’s push into data centers, power projects, and water infrastructure in the Permian Basin.
